!!! ATTENTION !!! READ IT CAREFULLY !!!

This menu entry will undo the cable-client connection configuration. If you proceed, TorBox will again accept wireless clients, but not wired clients (this is the default behavior).

IMPORTANT
- Choosing this menu entry will change the basic configuration of your
  TorBox and shut it down.
- After the shut down, you have to connect TorBox with a wireless
  connection.
- After the shut down, you will not be able to connect your TorBox with
  a wired client (via ethernet cable).
